  "elapsed_s": 258.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But I mean, I bought a car when I had cash stored.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I worked hard, and I had enough money.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But I bought a car.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "To make the story short, he took me to Milwaukee.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And then, when you are a refugee, you'll come-- there's four people who says, what city are you?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And then one asked the other one, what city are you?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And you say you are from a town like that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Do you know anybody from my town?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I mean, how are you going-- there's no communication.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "There is no telephone.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "So you would-- by the people, between the people, you communicate and find out what town they are, or who is alive now of what and everything.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "That's why-- or you put your name in wherever you go.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "You put your name, and people, you know, at certain places like in the kibbutz, or some other kibbutz.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And they check.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And then you come, the first thing you check to see-- who is alive.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And that's-- what did I say now?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "I forgot.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
